{"tid":1589064,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔好掛住笑差婆，軍情極為不利。","createTime":"2019-09-23T06:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T07:49:36.000Z","uid":301820,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7187363a28259e8f5a9c4b149b691ba397f03f","tid":1589064,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"軍警新戰術-狗閪臥底。<br />\n手法賤格無恥，但相當有效。<br />\n<br />\n1. 狗囡好少有人留意。<br />\n2. 就算發現囡狗臥底，佢發難打人，（畫面上）會得到大眾體諒。<br />\n而且當場有狗公同左膠會阻止。<br />\n3.利用no one leave behind ,其實臥底每次不斷拖慢大家撒離進度。（男義士走得慢遇左死，女義士行得慢只能叫佢先走，勇武只能用火魔法去擋。）<br />\n4.狗囡被捕（唔話自己人）引起勇武同情，間接挑釁示威者衝擊警方。（救囡）<br />\n5. 示威者通常靠囡囡報告戰線，狗囡亂報軍情引發送頭<br />\n<br />\n示威者心態一定要改，對家手法愈來愈低劣，針對勇武捨己救人。<br />\n<br />\n我相信連仔會諗到解決辦法，香港人加油啊！"},{"pid":"b1dd35fb3bad5c68070ca90718f9f522ca1ccd52","tid":1589064,"uid":325882,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40b4ac72be798894aa67ebed3e19ee3106b989be","tid":1589064,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"c0affedfd4e55a027ef1669177a8232c7c9e21fe","tid":1589064,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:17:35.000Z","msg":"其實好易 我地女手足係靚女d <br />\nd狗成個tb咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d7271c9be833b3186980b7c41782cb82696623","tid":1589064,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"8fe7650c45ffa4350dcea0446424e7abbc942b84","tid":1589064,"uid":68868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:19:35.000Z","msg":"唔覺得有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s